Case 1:20-cr-00330-PAE Document 542 Filed 12/14/21 Page 1 of 1
UNITED STATES DISTRICT COURT SOUTHERN DISTRICT OF NEW YORK
United States of America,
-v-
Ghislaine Maxwell,
Defendant.
ALISON J. NATHAN, District Judge:
The Court is in receipt of the Defense's letter dated December 13, 2021, regarding anticipated witnesses. The Government is ORDERED to submit a response no later than today, December 14, 2021, at 10:00 p.m. The Defense is FURTHER ORDERED to provide a copy of its anticipated witness order to the Court no later than today, December 14, 2021, at 12:00 p.m.
SO ORDERED.
Dated: December 14, 2021 New York, New York
ALISON J. NATHAN United States District Judge
